Go and download Node.js from the official website: https://nodejs.org/en/download/

https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/
After downloading the Node.js, you can check the version of Node.js by running the following command in the terminal:

    ```bash
    node -v
    ```
    ```bash
    npm -v
    ```
    ```bash
    npm install -g npm@latest
    ```
